title: Collectives Update: Vote! Vote! Vote!
description: Below are some of the artists from Indonesia who submitted their work to HUG 100 Artists to Watch. Help them by vote for their work.
author: zortan

body.raw:
## VOTE VOTE VOTE

Below are some of the artists from Indonesia who submitted their work to HUG 100 Artists to Watch. Help them by vote for their work here: [Vote! Vote! Vote!](https://thehug.xyz/open-calls/100-artists-to-watch-2024/vote)

Vote is easy! üôÇ
